    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Conversion of carbon-containing organic matter into carbon or carbonic residue. The formation of coal is an example of carbonization.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
